{"tid":2274554,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打明年初起員工可正式申請在家工作","createTime":"2020-11-06T13:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T00:09:08.000Z","uid":230530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"912f6258b79b9f20e6dff94aba11e52e0704ba0e","tid":2274554,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:28:38.000Z","msg":"渣打銀行表示，期望到2021年底前讓大約一半市場都能夠採取混合工作模式，員工可以選擇在家工作，在辦公室工作，或混合模式，即部分日子在辦公室工作，部分日子在家工作。集團並致力在2023年前讓90%員工能採取彈性工作模式，涉及55個市場中約7.5萬名員工。<br />\n<br />\n渣打說，由明年初開始，9個市場，包括香港同英國的員工，可以正式申請靈活工作模式安排。其餘階段會在明年第4季同2022年中推出。屆時員工可以對工作時間，包括工作時數同日數，以及地點有更多選擇。集團預計大部分員工將選擇混合模式。<br />\n<br />\n渣打說，上月向參與第一階段計劃9個市場的員工收集意見，同時亦檢視整間銀行所有工種，發現逾80%工種適合更多靈活安排。"},{"pid":"8e3fcae19c916d7b59bbddbf77e3248a642686ea","tid":2274554,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"可以移民英國 connect去香港work from england<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dbc372c3e277a583b35d98d460277f09b7f20f","tid":2274554,"uid":360430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e9031b63d4ad10a3c12344ee613749cee3ac7bd","tid":2274554,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"揸兜有咁好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175f2dc27aa66450165fbb263c5031610b473102","tid":2274554,"uid":304769,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8e3fcae19c916d7b59bbddbf77e3248a642686ea","tid":2274554,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"可以移民英國 connect去香港work from england<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"咪傻，擺明想炒香港人換支那人，work from 支那啦"},{"pid":"09538086c918344f01bc95b5aaf3e10ecc6831fe","tid":2274554,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:33:49.000Z","msg":"在家工作即係等如24小時on call"},{"pid":"47644d6b03dbfb4d13262576a7841b8aaa0dba2b","tid":2274554,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00b8a22c67afa8de618e089022e841f7d9b3533","tid":2274554,"uid":96321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b7dc7795d0d04bff676a43271ba6a6275925c3","tid":2274554,"uid":73546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T21:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c2c2b97ad335f8ce96248db6724ea371fe7c14","tid":2274554,"uid":237558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T00:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}